A reusable Django app that uses django-treebeard to create a threadedcomments Framework, following up notifications and comments that only hits the database after users confirm them by email.Real-time comment updates are also available using firebase as a notification mechanism of comment updates. Clients can connect to firebase for updates, and then query the backend for the actual changes, so that all data is located in the backend database.


